Paper: hep-th/0109052

Date: 2001-09-06

Title: Dynamics of the spinning particle in one dimension

Authors: W. Machin

Comments: 14 pages, ams-latex, references added

The most general N=1 Lagrangian for the spinning particle with localsupersymmetry is found and the constraints of the system are analysed. TheDirac quantisation of the model is also investigated.